00:01:43.340 --> 00:01:45.340
What about it?

00:01:45.340 --> 00:01:48.340
Are you a joyful person?

00:01:48.340 --> 00:01:50.340
What good is it?

00:01:51.340 --> 00:01:57.340
Well, the Bible says a joyful heart makes for a cheerful countenance.

00:01:57.340 --> 00:02:05.340
