00:02:23.340 --> 00:02:27.340
You smile and say, good.

00:02:27.340 --> 00:02:31.340
Your back, feet, and legs are killing you.

00:02:31.340 --> 00:02:38.340
But your heart won't let you give a negative answer.

00:02:38.340 --> 00:02:42.340
There are other more important reasons to be joyful.

00:02:43.340 --> 00:02:45.340
Here's one.

00:02:45.340 --> 00:02:49.340
Jehovah is a joyful person.

00:02:49.340 --> 00:02:53.340
