00:02:56.340 --> 00:03:01.340
Now, a synonym is the joyful God.

00:03:01.340 --> 00:03:05.340
He rejoices in his work.

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:07.340
Well, how do we know that?

00:03:07.340 --> 00:03:13.340
Well, look at the 104th Psalm and verse 31.

00:03:13.340 --> 00:03:18.340
The glory of Jehovah will last forever.

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:23.340
Jehovah will rejoice in his works.

00:03:23.340 --> 00:03:27.340
Jehovah will rejoice in his work.

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:34.340
