00:03:34.340 --> 00:03:39.340
Now, secondly, Jesus, too, is a happy worker.

00:03:39.340 --> 00:03:45.340
At 1 Timothy chapter 6 and verse 14 and 15,

00:03:45.340 --> 00:03:49.340
