00:04:02.340 --> 00:04:10.139
To do your will, oh my God, is my delight.

00:04:10.139 --> 00:04:15.139
Now, this means to please greatly.

00:04:15.139 --> 00:04:19.139
According to John chapter 4 and verse 34,

00:04:19.139 --> 00:04:23.139
