00:04:23.139 --> 00:04:28.139
It energized him and sustained him.

00:04:28.139 --> 00:04:35.860
Doing God's will was like butter on his bread and milk in his glass.

00:04:35.860 --> 00:04:41.720
Jehovah wants us to rejoice in our work.

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:43.720
Read with me, please.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:48.720
