00:24:08.779 --> 00:24:10.779
Planning for the new Patterson Visitor Center

00:24:10.779 --> 00:24:12.779
began in 2018.

00:24:12.779 --> 00:24:14.779
A project development group

00:24:14.779 --> 00:24:16.779
was formed with a goal

00:24:16.779 --> 00:24:18.779
of starting construction,

00:24:18.779 --> 00:24:20.779
but unforeseen challenges

00:24:20.779 --> 00:24:22.779
were about to occur.

00:24:22.779 --> 00:24:24.779
In March of 2020,

00:24:24.779 --> 00:24:26.779
an outbreak of COVID-19 in the New York

00:24:26.779 --> 00:24:28.779
area caused Bethel to go

00:24:28.779 --> 00:24:30.779
into a full lockdown.

00:24:30.779 --> 00:24:32.779
How did the design group

00:24:32.779 --> 00:24:34.779
siege Jehovah's blessing on the project

00:24:34.779 --> 00:24:36.779
during this unprecedented time?

00:24:36.779 --> 00:24:40.099
Well, when Bethel locked down

00:24:40.099 --> 00:24:42.099
and suspended in-person meetings,

00:24:42.099 --> 00:24:44.099
so did the town of Patterson.

00:24:44.099 --> 00:24:46.099
This created a series

00:24:46.099 --> 00:24:48.099
challenge for us to obtain

00:24:48.099 --> 00:24:50.099
the necessary approvals

00:24:50.099 --> 00:24:52.099
and to keep the project moving forward.

00:24:52.099 --> 00:24:54.099
So with a threat of falling

00:24:54.099 --> 00:24:56.099
months behind,

00:24:56.099 --> 00:24:58.099
we had to rely on Jehovah

00:24:58.099 --> 00:25:00.099
and alter our approach.

00:25:00.099 --> 00:25:02.099
So a local elder was given

00:25:02.099 --> 00:25:04.099
permission to attend the town

00:25:04.099 --> 00:25:06.099
and opened up.

00:25:06.099 --> 00:25:08.099
He allowed us as a design team

00:25:08.099 --> 00:25:10.099
to make a presentation effectively

00:25:10.099 --> 00:25:12.099
but remotely.

00:25:12.099 --> 00:25:14.099
We saw Jehovah's hand

00:25:14.099 --> 00:25:16.099
and his blessing on this entire arrangement.

00:25:16.099 --> 00:25:18.099
So through months of meetings,

00:25:18.099 --> 00:25:20.099
we were able to get the approvals needed

00:25:20.099 --> 00:25:22.099
and then get a building permit

00:25:22.099 --> 00:25:24.099
to begin construction

00:25:24.099 --> 00:25:28.430
all of this taking place

00:25:28.430 --> 00:25:30.430
during the lockdown.

00:25:30.430 --> 00:25:32.430
Following all the local guidelines,

00:25:32.430 --> 00:25:34.430
the branch found a way

00:25:34.430 --> 00:25:36.430
to properly

00:25:36.430 --> 00:25:38.430
so they could work on the project.

00:25:38.430 --> 00:25:40.430
Jehovah caused many volunteers

00:25:40.430 --> 00:25:45.019
to offer themselves willingly

00:25:45.019 --> 00:25:47.019
to help.

00:25:47.019 --> 00:25:49.019
Here we are building

00:25:49.019 --> 00:25:51.019
the Patterson Visitor Center

00:25:51.019 --> 00:25:53.019
during a most unique time in history

00:25:53.019 --> 00:25:55.019
in the midst of a global pandemic.

00:25:55.019 --> 00:25:57.019
The Brotherhood

00:25:57.019 --> 00:25:59.019
has demonstrated a heart for the work.

00:25:59.019 --> 00:26:01.019
Through contributions,

00:26:01.019 --> 00:26:03.019
brothers and sisters offering their skills,

00:26:03.019 --> 00:26:05.019
some of which are quite unique.

00:26:05.019 --> 00:26:07.019
It's so encouraging to see

00:26:07.019 --> 00:26:09.019
how Jehovah has come to our aid

00:26:09.019 --> 00:26:11.019
with supply issues

00:26:11.019 --> 00:26:13.019
and how Bethel departments

00:26:13.019 --> 00:26:15.019
have cooperated and provided

00:26:15.019 --> 00:26:17.019
skilled people to help us.

00:26:17.019 --> 00:26:19.019
It's been so encouraging.

00:26:19.019 --> 00:26:21.019
All involved have seen Jehovah's hand

00:26:21.019 --> 00:26:23.019
guiding the way through these

00:26:23.019 --> 00:26:25.019
challenging circumstances.

00:26:25.019 --> 00:26:27.019
But some may wonder,

00:26:27.019 --> 00:26:29.019
at a time when guests are not allowed

00:26:29.019 --> 00:26:31.019
