to come the praiseworthy deeds

00:54:36.739 --> 00:54:38.739
and the wonderful things

00:54:38.739 --> 00:54:40.739
that He has done.

00:54:40.739 --> 00:54:42.739
Well, now,

00:54:42.739 --> 00:54:44.739
this includes more

00:54:44.739 --> 00:54:46.739
than just the basic truths.

00:54:46.739 --> 00:54:48.739
It also includes all

00:54:48.739 --> 00:54:50.739
of the wonderful things

00:54:50.739 --> 00:54:52.739
that we've been taught

00:54:52.739 --> 00:54:54.739
by other brothers and sisters.

00:54:54.739 --> 00:54:56.739
All the experiences

00:54:56.739 --> 00:54:58.739
that we've had

00:54:58.739 --> 00:55:00.739
in experiencing the hand

00:55:00.739 --> 00:55:02.739
of Jehovah in our own lives.

00:55:02.739 --> 00:55:04.739
Well, Jehovah took the matter

00:55:04.739 --> 00:55:06.739
of passing this on

00:55:06.739 --> 00:55:08.739
to the next generation

00:55:08.739 --> 00:55:10.739
very seriously,

00:55:10.739 --> 00:55:12.739
because look at what it says in verse 5.

00:55:12.739 --> 00:55:14.739
It says,

00:55:14.739 --> 00:55:16.739
he established a reminder

00:55:16.739 --> 00:55:18.739
in Jacob

00:55:18.739 --> 00:55:20.739
and set a law

00:55:20.739 --> 00:55:22.739
in Israel.

00:55:22.739 --> 00:55:24.739
He commanded our forefathers

00:55:24.739 --> 00:55:26.739
to make these things known

00:55:26.739 --> 00:55:28.739
to their children

00:55:28.739 --> 00:55:30.739
so that the next generation

00:55:30.739 --> 00:55:32.739
the children yet to be

00:55:32.739 --> 00:55:34.739
they in turn would relate them

00:55:34.739 --> 00:55:36.739
to their children.

00:55:36.739 --> 00:55:38.739
Well, brothers and sisters,

00:55:38.739 --> 00:55:40.739
especially those of you

00:55:40.739 --> 00:55:42.739
who have so much wisdom

00:55:42.739 --> 00:55:44.739
and experience,

00:55:44.739 --> 00:55:46.739
do you feel

00:55:46.739 --> 00:55:48.739
that responsibility

00:55:48.739 --> 00:55:50.739
to share what you have

00:55:50.739 --> 00:55:52.739
with the generation to come?

00:55:52.739 --> 00:55:54.739
Well, if we get the sense

00:55:54.739 --> 00:55:56.739
of Deuteronomy 29-29

00:55:56.739 --> 00:55:58.739
and Psalm 78,

00:55:58.739 --> 00:56:00.739
well, then we will do this.

00:56:00.739 --> 00:56:02.739
We will share what we have

00:56:02.739 --> 00:56:04.739
with the next generation.

00:56:04.739 --> 00:56:06.739
But how do we do it?

00:56:06.739 --> 00:56:08.739
Well, of course, this process begins

00:56:08.739 --> 00:56:10.739
with all of our parents.

00:56:10.739 --> 00:56:12.739
And by their following

00:56:12.739 --> 00:56:14.739
the command in Deuteronomy 6,

00:56:14.739 --> 00:56:16.739
verses 6 and 7,

00:56:16.739 --> 00:56:18.739
to teach their children

00:56:18.739 --> 00:56:20.739
as they sit in the house,

00:56:20.739 --> 00:56:22.739
as they walk on the road

00:56:22.739 --> 00:56:24.739
when they lie down

00:56:24.739 --> 00:56:26.739
and when they get up.

00:56:26.739 --> 00:56:28.739
But the process

00:56:28.739 --> 00:56:30.739
does not end

00:56:30.739 --> 00:56:32.739
with the Christian parents.

00:56:32.739 --> 00:56:34.739
We also have a

00:56:34.739 --> 00:56:36.739
responsibility to teach

00:56:36.739 --> 00:56:38.739
and train young adults

00:56:38.739 --> 00:56:40.739
so that they can take

00:56:40.739 --> 00:56:42.739
on responsibility

00:56:42.739 --> 00:56:44.739
in Jehovah's congregation.

00:56:44.739 --> 00:56:46.739
Now, the Bible

00:56:46.739 --> 00:56:48.739
is filled with examples

00:56:48.739 --> 00:56:50.739
of individuals who are wonderful trainers.

00:56:50.739 --> 00:56:52.739
Maybe one who comes to mind

00:56:52.739 --> 00:56:54.739
right away is Moses.

00:56:54.739 --> 00:56:56.739
It seems that in the Bible

00:56:56.739 --> 00:56:58.739
wherever you see Moses,

00:56:58.739 --> 00:57:00.739
you see Joshua.

00:57:00.739 --> 00:57:02.739
They're always together.

00:57:02.739 --> 00:57:04.739
Can you imagine the wonderful training

00:57:04.739 --> 00:57:06.739
that Moses was able to impart

00:57:06.739 --> 00:57:08.739
to Joshua as they work

00:57:08.739 --> 00:57:10.739
together for more than 40 years?

00:57:10.739 --> 00:57:14.739
Moses not only told Joshua

00:57:14.739 --> 00:57:16.739
but he also showed him.

00:57:16.739 --> 00:57:18.739
And by being with him,

00:57:18.739 --> 00:57:20.739
he was able to observe

00:57:20.739 --> 00:57:22.739
his fine example.

00:57:22.739 --> 00:57:24.739
Well, when the time was ready,

00:57:24.739 --> 00:57:26.739
when Moses was ready

00:57:26.739 --> 00:57:28.739
to hand over the responsibility,

00:57:28.739 --> 00:57:30.739
notice what he says here

00:57:30.739 --> 00:57:32.739
in Deuteronomy chapter 31

00:57:32.739 --> 00:57:36.150
and verse 7.

00:57:36.150 --> 00:57:40.150
It says Moses then called Joshua

00:57:40.150 --> 00:57:42.150
and said to him before the eyes

00:57:42.150 --> 00:57:44.150
of all Israel,

00:57:44.150 --> 00:57:46.150
be courageous and strong

00:57:46.150 --> 00:57:48.150
for you are the one

00:57:48.150 --> 00:57:50.150
who will bring this people into the land

00:57:50.150 --> 00:57:52.150
that Jehovah swore to their forefathers

00:57:52.150 --> 00:57:54.150
to give to them

00:57:54.150 --> 00:57:56.150
and you will give it to them

00:57:56.150 --> 00:57:58.150
as an inheritance.

00:57:58.150 --> 00:58:00.150
Jehovah is the one marching

00:58:00.150 --> 00:58:02.150
before you and he will continue

00:58:02.150 --> 00:58:04.150
with you.

00:58:04.150 --> 00:58:06.150
He will neither desert you

00:58:06.150 --> 00:58:08.150
nor abandon you.

00:58:08.150 --> 00:58:10.150
Do not be afraid or be terrified.

00:58:10.150 --> 00:58:12.150
Well, can you imagine

00:58:12.150 --> 00:58:14.150
how Moses must have felt

00:58:14.150 --> 00:58:16.150
to say those words to this young man

00:58:16.150 --> 00:58:18.150
who he had worked so hard

00:58:18.150 --> 00:58:20.150
all of these years with?

00:58:20.150 --> 00:58:22.150
Well, that's not the only example

00:58:22.150 --> 00:58:24.150
that's in the scriptures.

00:58:24.150 --> 00:58:26.150
What about Paul and Timothy?

00:58:26.150 --> 00:58:28.150
We know that Timothy was

00:58:28.150 --> 00:58:30.150
probably in his late teens

00:58:30.150 --> 00:58:32.150
or early 20s

00:58:32.150 --> 00:58:34.150
when Paul met him at Listera.

00:58:34.150 --> 00:58:36.150
What did Paul do?

00:58:36.150 --> 00:58:38.150
He took that young man along with him

00:58:38.150 --> 00:58:40.150
on his tours,

00:58:40.150 --> 00:58:42.150
going from congregation to congregation.

00:58:42.150 --> 00:58:44.150
He put him in mind

00:58:44.150 --> 00:58:46.150
of his methods.

00:58:46.150 --> 00:58:48.150
He taught him.

00:58:48.150 --> 00:58:50.150
And as a result,

00:58:50.150 --> 00:58:54.150
a solid, mature Christian man

00:58:54.150 --> 00:58:56.150
who was able to strengthen

00:58:56.150 --> 00:58:58.150
the congregations of God's people.

00:58:58.150 --> 00:59:00.150
Do you remember what Paul said about him

00:59:00.150 --> 00:59:02.150
in Philippians chapter 2?

00:59:02.150 --> 00:59:04.150
It's quite a recommendation.

00:59:04.150 --> 00:59:06.150
Philippians chapter 2

00:59:06.150 --> 00:59:10.150
and verse 20.

00:59:10.150 --> 00:59:14.150
Paul said, for I have no one else

00:59:14.150 --> 00:59:16.150
of a disposition like his

00:59:16.150 --> 00:59:18.150
who will genuinely care

00:59:18.150 --> 00:59:20.150
for your concerns.

00:59:20.150 --> 00:59:22.150
What a tremendous

00:59:22.150 --> 00:59:24.150
recommendation.

00:59:24.150 --> 00:59:26.150
But because Paul had invested that

00:59:26.150 --> 00:59:28.150
time into Timothy,

00:59:28.150 --> 00:59:30.150
he knew the fine qualities

00:59:30.150 --> 00:59:32.150
that young man had.

00:59:32.150 --> 00:59:34.150
Well, Paul not only wanted Timothy

00:59:34.150 --> 00:59:36.150
to take that training himself,

00:59:36.150 --> 00:59:38.150
but you'll recall

00:59:38.150 --> 00:59:40.150
that in 2 Timothy chapter 2,

00:59:40.150 --> 00:59:44.150
he gave advice to Timothy

00:59:44.150 --> 00:59:46.150
as to what he was to do

00:59:46.150 --> 00:59:48.150
with all of that fine training

00:59:48.150 --> 00:59:50.150
that he had received.

00:59:50.150 --> 00:59:52.150
2 Timothy chapter 2

00:59:52.150 --> 00:59:54.150
and verse 2,

00:59:54.150 --> 00:59:56.150
Paul said,

00:59:56.150 --> 00:59:58.150
and the things you heard from me

00:59:58.150 --> 01:00:00.150
that were supported by many witnesses,

01:00:00.150 --> 01:00:02.150
these things

01:00:02.150 --> 01:00:04.150
in trust to faithful men

01:00:04.150 --> 01:00:06.150
who in turn

01:00:06.150 --> 01:00:08.150
will be adequately qualified

01:00:08.150 --> 01:00:10.150
to teach others.

01:00:10.150 --> 01:00:12.150
So that training

01:00:12.150 --> 01:00:14.150
would go on to future brothers

01:00:14.150 --> 01:00:16.150
and future generations

01:00:16.150 --> 01:00:18.150
of servants of Jehovah.

01:00:18.150 --> 01:00:20.150
Paul invested training

01:00:20.150 --> 01:00:22.150
in a very young man

01:00:22.150 --> 01:00:24.150
and it paid off.

01:00:24.150 --> 01:00:26.150
In our modern day,

01:00:26.150 --> 01:00:30.150
I think of Brother Nathan Moore

01:00:30.150 --> 01:00:32.150
as an outstanding trainer.

01:00:32.150 --> 01:00:34.150
When he became the president

01:00:34.150 --> 01:00:36.150
of the Watchtower Society

01:00:36.150 --> 01:00:38.150
in January of 1942,

01:00:38.150 --> 01:00:42.150
he was only 36 years old.

01:00:42.150 --> 01:00:44.150
Now, he could have thought,

01:00:44.150 --> 01:00:46.150
I'm so young.

01:00:46.150 --> 01:00:48.150
I have many, many years ahead of me

01:00:48.150 --> 01:00:50.150
to be able to care for matters.

01:00:50.150 --> 01:00:52.150
And so there really isn't any need

01:00:52.150 --> 01:00:54.150
to train others.

01:00:54.150 --> 01:00:56.150
But Brother Nor did not have

01:00:56.150 --> 01:00:58.150
that disposition.

01:00:58.150 --> 01:01:00.150
He was a trainer

01:01:00.150 --> 01:01:02.150
even at that young age.

01:01:02.150 --> 01:01:04.150
He assigned Brother Milton Henshel

01:01:04.150 --> 01:01:08.150
who was in his mid-twenties

01:01:08.150 --> 01:01:10.150
to be his secretary.

01:01:10.150 --> 01:01:12.150
Brother Nor took Brother Henshel

01:01:12.150 --> 01:01:14.150
with him on his travels

01:01:14.150 --> 01:01:16.150
all over the world to branches

01:01:16.150 --> 01:01:18.150
and missionary homes

01:01:18.150 --> 01:01:20.150
to strengthen the brothers.

01:01:20.150 --> 01:01:22.150
He had him right by his side

01:01:22.150 --> 01:01:24.150
at major conventions

01:01:24.150 --> 01:01:26.150
not just telling him

01:01:26.150 --> 01:01:28.150
but showing him

01:01:28.150 --> 01:01:30.150
how to take the lead.

01:01:30.150 --> 01:01:32.150
And Brother Henshel

01:01:32.150 --> 01:01:34.150
absorbed that training.

01:01:34.150 --> 01:01:36.150
By 1947,

01:01:36.150 --> 01:01:38.150
he was a member of the board of directors

01:01:38.150 --> 01:01:40.150
of the Watchtower Society,

01:01:40.150 --> 01:01:42.150
only 27 years old.

01:01:42.150 --> 01:01:44.150
And he went on to serve

01:01:44.150 --> 01:01:46.150
as a member of the governing body.

01:01:46.150 --> 01:01:48.150
Brother Nor trained other young brothers

01:01:48.150 --> 01:01:50.150
like Don Adams.

01:01:50.150 --> 01:01:52.150
This photo

01:01:52.150 --> 01:01:54.150
that we're about to show

01:01:54.150 --> 01:01:56.150
was taken at a gathering

01:01:56.150 --> 01:02:00.150
on Brother Adams' 70th anniversary

01:02:00.150 --> 01:02:02.150
in full-time service.

01:02:02.150 --> 01:02:04.150
Now, here you see

01:02:04.150 --> 01:02:06.150
a group of young men

01:02:06.150 --> 01:02:08.150
who had trained Robert Wallen,

01:02:08.150 --> 01:02:10.150
Charles Mollahan,

01:02:10.150 --> 01:02:12.150
Davidson Claire,

01:02:12.150 --> 01:02:14.150
and Don Adams.

01:02:14.150 --> 01:02:16.150
All of these men were identified

01:02:16.150 --> 01:02:18.150
when they were very young

01:02:18.150 --> 01:02:20.150
and they worked together

01:02:20.150 --> 01:02:22.150
for more than 50 years faithfully.

01:02:22.150 --> 01:02:24.150
Jehovah helped Brother Nor

01:02:24.150 --> 01:02:28.150
to choose very well.

01:02:28.150 --> 01:02:30.150
But it didn't end there.

01:02:30.150 --> 01:02:32.150
Brother Nor also appointed

01:02:32.150 --> 01:02:34.150
well-qualified young brothers

01:02:34.150 --> 01:02:36.150
who were gillied graduates

01:02:36.150 --> 01:02:38.150
to assignments with great responsibility.

01:02:38.150 --> 01:02:40.150
For example,

01:02:40.150 --> 01:02:42.150
Brother Kenneth Little

01:02:42.150 --> 01:02:44.150
was assigned to be the branch servant

01:02:44.150 --> 01:02:48.150
in Canada when he was 34 years old.

01:02:48.150 --> 01:02:50.150
Brother Denson Hopkinsven

01:02:50.150 --> 01:02:52.150
was assigned as the branch servant

01:02:52.150 --> 01:02:54.150
in the Philippines

01:02:54.150 --> 01:02:56.150
when he was 33 years old.

01:02:56.150 --> 01:02:58.150
And Brother Richard Kelsey

01:02:58.150 --> 01:03:00.150
was assigned as the branch servant

01:03:00.150 --> 01:03:02.150
in Germany

01:03:02.150 --> 01:03:04.150
when he was 38.

01:03:04.150 --> 01:03:06.150
When appointed,

01:03:06.150 --> 01:03:08.150
Brother Kelsey said to Brother Nor,

01:03:08.150 --> 01:03:10.150
but I'm only 38.

01:03:10.150 --> 01:03:12.150
And Brother Nor said,

01:03:12.150 --> 01:03:14.150
well, yeah, that's about the age I was

01:03:14.150 --> 01:03:17.719
when I became president.

01:03:17.719 --> 01:03:19.719
Brother Nor once again had chosen well.

01:03:19.719 --> 01:03:21.719
Those last three brothers

01:03:21.719 --> 01:03:23.719
are all still serving

01:03:23.719 --> 01:03:25.719
on the branch committees

01:03:25.719 --> 01:03:27.719
in their respective lands

01:03:27.719 --> 01:03:29.719
and are all members

01:03:29.719 --> 01:03:31.719
of the Watchtower Bible

01:03:31.719 --> 01:03:33.719
and are tied in today for this meeting.

01:03:33.719 --> 01:03:50.019
Isn't that wonderful?

01:03:50.019 --> 01:03:52.019
But there's a lesson here, brothers.

01:03:52.019 --> 01:03:54.019
There's a lesson.

01:03:54.019 --> 01:03:56.019
Brother Nor expressed confidence

01:03:56.019 --> 01:03:58.019
in humble young brothers.

01:03:58.019 --> 01:04:00.019
He allowed them

01:04:00.019 --> 01:04:02.019
to take on responsibility

01:04:02.019 --> 01:04:04.019
and that proved to be

01:04:04.019 --> 01:04:06.019
a wonderful blessing

01:04:06.019 --> 01:04:08.019
for Jehovah's people.

01:04:08.019 --> 01:04:10.019
Well, what's the lesson then

01:04:10.019 --> 01:04:12.019
for elders,

01:04:12.019 --> 01:04:14.019
for circuit overseers,

01:04:14.019 --> 01:04:16.019
for all mature brothers

01:04:16.019 --> 01:04:18.019
in the congregation?

01:04:18.019 --> 01:04:20.019
We must actively

01:04:20.019 --> 01:04:22.019
be training and teaching

01:04:22.019 --> 01:04:24.019
the next generation

01:04:24.019 --> 01:04:26.019
of ministerial servants,

01:04:26.019 --> 01:04:28.019
the next generation

01:04:28.019 --> 01:04:30.019
of elders,

01:04:30.019 --> 01:04:32.019
the next generation

01:04:32.019 --> 01:04:34.019
of circuit overseers.

01:04:34.019 --> 01:04:36.019
And we must take this responsibility

01:04:36.019 --> 01:04:38.019
seriously.

01:04:38.019 --> 01:04:40.019
Because the truth

01:04:40.019 --> 01:04:42.019
belongs not just to us.

01:04:42.019 --> 01:04:44.019
It also belongs to our sons

01:04:44.019 --> 01:04:46.019
to our descendants.

01:04:46.019 --> 01:04:48.019
We must pass on

01:04:48.019 --> 01:04:50.019
the truth,

01:04:50.019 --> 01:04:52.019
the wisdom,

01:04:52.019 --> 01:04:54.019
the experience that we have

01:04:54.019 --> 01:04:56.019
in our treasure store

01:04:56.019 --> 01:04:58.019
to these next Joshua's,

01:04:58.019 --> 01:05:00.019
these next Timothy's

01:05:00.019 --> 01:05:02.019
that Jehovah will raise up.

01:05:02.019 --> 01:05:04.019
But now that's the role

01:05:04.019 --> 01:05:06.019
of the trainers.

01:05:06.019 --> 01:05:08.019
What is the role

01:05:08.019 --> 01:05:10.019
of you younger brothers

01:05:10.019 --> 01:05:11.019
who are listening to this program?

01:05:11.019 --> 01:05:13.019
Well, it's your responsibility

01:05:13.019 --> 01:05:15.019
to work hard,

01:05:15.019 --> 01:05:17.019
to meet the scriptural qualifications

01:05:17.019 --> 01:05:19.019
for ministerial servants

01:05:19.019 --> 01:05:21.019
and later for elders.

01:05:21.019 --> 01:05:23.019
Seek out training.

01:05:23.019 --> 01:05:25.019
Ask for advice.

01:05:25.019 --> 01:05:27.019
Ask for counsel.

01:05:27.019 --> 01:05:29.019
Be eager

01:05:29.019 --> 01:05:31.019
to learn from older brothers

01:05:31.019 --> 01:05:33.019
who are rich in wisdom

01:05:33.019 --> 01:05:35.019
and experience.

01:05:35.019 --> 01:05:37.019
Now, to help you grow

01:05:37.019 --> 01:05:39.019
those brothers

01:05:39.019 --> 01:05:41.019
who are rich in wisdom

01:05:41.019 --> 01:05:43.019
and experience.

01:05:43.019 --> 01:05:45.019
They may even correct you

01:05:45.019 --> 01:05:47.019
from time to time.

01:05:47.019 --> 01:05:49.019
Will you love them

01:05:49.019 --> 01:05:51.019
for doing that?

01:05:51.019 --> 01:05:53.019
Like Jacob,

01:05:53.019 --> 01:05:55.019
who wrestled with an angel

01:05:55.019 --> 01:05:57.019
to receive a blessing,

01:05:57.019 --> 01:05:59.019
you too may have to wrestle.

01:05:59.019 --> 01:06:01.019
You may have to struggle

01:06:01.019 --> 01:06:03.019
at times to get that blessing,

01:06:03.019 --> 01:06:05.019
to reach that goal.

01:06:05.019 --> 01:06:07.019
But if you work hard

01:06:07.019 --> 01:06:09.019
you will grow spiritually.

01:06:09.019 --> 01:06:11.019
You will draw close to him

01:06:11.019 --> 01:06:13.019
and who knows what

01:06:13.019 --> 01:06:15.019
responsibilities

01:06:15.019 --> 01:06:17.019
may come to you.

01:06:17.019 --> 01:06:19.019
What is the governing body

01:06:19.019 --> 01:06:21.019
doing to support efforts

01:06:21.019 --> 01:06:23.019
to train young brothers?

01:06:23.019 --> 01:06:25.019
Well, in January of this year

01:06:25.019 --> 01:06:27.019
the governing body requested

01:06:27.019 --> 01:06:29.019
all bodies of elders

01:06:29.019 --> 01:06:31.019
worldwide

01:06:31.019 --> 01:06:33.019
to give priority to helping

01:06:33.019 --> 01:06:35.019
younger brothers grow

01:06:35.019 --> 01:06:37.019
congregation

01:06:37.019 --> 01:06:39.019
responsibilities.

01:06:39.019 --> 01:06:41.019
Elders and circuit overseers

01:06:41.019 --> 01:06:43.019
were reminded

01:06:43.019 --> 01:06:45.019
that young brothers

01:06:45.019 --> 01:06:47.019
who applied themselves

01:06:47.019 --> 01:06:49.019
may qualify

01:06:49.019 --> 01:06:51.019
as ministerial servants

01:06:51.019 --> 01:06:53.019
in their late teens.

01:06:53.019 --> 01:06:55.019
And that an exceptional

01:06:55.019 --> 01:06:57.019
ministerial servant

01:06:57.019 --> 01:06:59.019
who has gained experience

01:06:59.019 --> 01:07:01.019
in shepherding and teaching

01:07:01.019 --> 01:07:03.019
could serve as an elder

01:07:03.019 --> 01:07:05.019
servant.

01:07:05.019 --> 01:07:07.019
Now here is another

01:07:07.019 --> 01:07:09.019
arrangement that we have

01:07:09.019 --> 01:07:11.019
not publicly announced before

01:07:11.019 --> 01:07:13.019
but we will today.

01:07:13.019 --> 01:07:15.019
Circuit overseers have

01:07:15.019 --> 01:07:17.019
also been informed

01:07:17.019 --> 01:07:19.019
that they may invite

01:07:19.019 --> 01:07:21.019
qualified young brothers

01:07:21.019 --> 01:07:23.019
between the ages of 21

01:07:23.019 --> 01:07:25.019
and 23

01:07:25.019 --> 01:07:27.019
to apply to attend the

01:07:27.019 --> 01:07:29.019
school for Kingdom

01:07:29.019 --> 01:07:31.019
evangelizers.

01:07:31.019 --> 01:07:33.019
But the efforts

01:07:33.019 --> 01:07:35.019
do not end there.

01:07:35.019 --> 01:07:37.019
Jehovah willing.

01:07:37.019 --> 01:07:39.019
In January 2023

01:07:39.019 --> 01:07:41.019
the School for Kingdom

01:07:41.019 --> 01:07:43.019
evangelizers will again

01:07:43.019 --> 01:07:45.019
begin functioning

01:07:45.019 --> 01:07:47.019
in-person worldwide.

01:07:47.019 --> 01:07:49.019
And as we resume

01:07:49.019 --> 01:07:51.019
in-person regional conventions,

01:07:51.019 --> 01:07:53.019
just imagine the joy

01:07:53.019 --> 01:07:55.019
that we'll have

01:07:55.019 --> 01:07:57.019
in seeing younger brothers

01:07:57.019 --> 01:07:59.019
get up and give their first

01:07:59.019 --> 01:08:01.019
talk at a regional convention.

01:08:01.019 --> 01:08:03.019
Won't that be wonderful?

01:08:03.019 --> 01:08:16.449
Are you looking forward to it?

01:08:16.449 --> 01:08:18.449
But the governing body has

01:08:18.449 --> 01:08:20.449
another new initiative.

01:08:20.449 --> 01:08:22.449
The governing body members

01:08:22.449 --> 01:08:24.449
will now have the possibility

01:08:24.449 --> 01:08:26.449
to take a younger brother

01:08:26.449 --> 01:08:28.449
along with them

01:08:28.449 --> 01:08:30.449
when they make shepherding visits

01:08:30.449 --> 01:08:32.449
to the branches.

01:08:32.449 --> 01:08:34.449
And appointed governing body

01:08:34.449 --> 01:08:36.449
helpers, who are headquarters

01:08:36.449 --> 01:08:38.449
representatives,

01:08:38.449 --> 01:08:40.449
when they make their branch

01:08:40.449 --> 01:08:42.449
visits.

01:08:42.449 --> 01:08:44.449
These arrangements

01:08:44.449 --> 01:08:46.449
will allow many brothers

01:08:46.449 --> 01:08:48.449
to receive additional training

01:08:48.449 --> 01:08:50.449
directly

01:08:50.449 --> 01:08:52.449
from governing body members

01:08:52.449 --> 01:08:54.449
and helpers.

01:08:54.449 --> 01:08:56.449
Well, what have we discussed

01:08:56.449 --> 01:08:58.449
in this brief talk?

01:08:58.449 --> 01:09:00.449
Jehovah has allowed us

01:09:00.449 --> 01:09:02.449
to know the truth.

01:09:02.449 --> 01:09:04.449
He's allowed us to be trained.

01:09:04.449 --> 01:09:06.449
He's allowed us to gain wisdom

01:09:06.449 --> 01:09:08.449
and helpers.

01:09:08.449 --> 01:09:10.449
What now is our responsibility?

01:09:10.449 --> 01:09:12.449
Well, let's read it

01:09:12.449 --> 01:09:14.449
in Psalm 71, because the psalmist

01:09:14.449 --> 01:09:16.449
put it so beautifully here.

01:09:16.449 --> 01:09:20.449
Psalm 71 and verse 17.

01:09:20.449 --> 01:09:24.449
Oh, God, you have taught me

01:09:24.449 --> 01:09:26.449
from my youth.

01:09:26.449 --> 01:09:28.449
And until now, I keep declaring

01:09:28.449 --> 01:09:30.449
your wonderful works.

01:09:30.449 --> 01:09:32.449
Even when I am old and gray,

01:09:32.449 --> 01:09:34.449
oh, God, do not abandon me.

01:09:34.449 --> 01:09:38.449
Let me tell the next generation

01:09:38.449 --> 01:09:40.449
about your power

01:09:40.449 --> 01:09:42.449
and about your mightiness

01:09:42.449 --> 01:09:46.449
to all those who are to come.

01:09:46.449 --> 01:09:48.449
Dear brothers, please,

01:09:48.449 --> 01:09:50.449
let us work hard

01:09:50.449 --> 01:09:52.449
to share the wonderful truths,

01:09:52.449 --> 01:09:54.449
the experience,

01:09:54.449 --> 01:09:56.449
the wisdom that we have gained

01:09:56.449 --> 01:10:00.449
with the generation to come.

01:10:00.449 --> 01:10:06.829
That certainly does

01:10:06.829 --> 01:10:08.829
meet a need, doesn't it?

01:10:08.829 --> 01:10:10.829
Very, very nice.

01:10:10.829 --> 01:10:12.829
Thank you, Mark.

01:10:12.829 --> 01:10:14.829
Now, how did you feel

01:10:14.829 --> 01:10:16.829
during the pandemic

01:10:16.829 --> 01:10:18.829
when you watched videos

01:10:18.829 --> 01:10:20.829
on GW Broadcasting?

01:10:20.829 --> 01:10:22.829
Of happy brothers and sisters

01:10:22.829 --> 01:10:24.829
going from door to door

01:10:24.829 --> 01:10:26.829
and doing artwork

01:10:26.829 --> 01:10:28.829
and conducting Bible studies,

01:10:28.829 --> 01:10:30.829
it made me kind of sad

01:10:30.829 --> 01:10:32.829
because I wanted to do that too.

01:10:32.829 --> 01:10:34.829
But we couldn't

01:10:34.829 --> 01:10:36.829
go into the pandemic.

01:10:36.829 --> 01:10:38.829
Well, now we have access

01:10:38.829 --> 01:10:40.829
to all of our features

01:10:40.829 --> 01:10:42.829
of the ministry.

01:10:42.829 --> 01:10:44.829
So I don't think any of us

01:10:44.829 --> 01:10:46.829
are going to be sad

01:10:46.829 --> 01:10:48.829
when watching the next video.

01:10:48.829 --> 01:10:50.829
It's going to trace the history

01:10:50.829 --> 01:10:52.829
of our preaching activity

01:10:52.829 --> 01:10:56.239
from 1919.

01:10:56.239 --> 01:10:58.239
It's great.

01:10:58.239 --> 01:11:00.239
One hundred years ago

01:11:00.239 --> 01:11:02.239
when our brothers and sisters

01:11:02.239 --> 01:11:04.239
were invited to the 1922

01:11:04.239 --> 01:11:06.239
to be excited.

01:11:06.239 --> 01:11:08.239
Why?

01:11:08.239 --> 01:11:10.239
You see, just three years earlier,

01:11:10.239 --> 01:11:12.239
they had been energized

01:11:12.239 --> 01:11:14.239
by a newly organized approach

01:11:14.239 --> 01:11:16.239
to preach the good news of the kingdom.

01:11:16.239 --> 01:11:18.239
The Bible Students Convention

01:11:18.239 --> 01:11:20.239
in 1919 launched

01:11:20.239 --> 01:11:22.239
a door-to-door campaign

01:11:22.239 --> 01:11:24.239
to obtain subscriptions

01:11:24.239 --> 01:11:26.239
to the newly released

01:11:26.239 --> 01:11:28.239
Golden Age magazine.

01:11:28.239 --> 01:11:30.239
Later that year, a service director

01:11:30.239 --> 01:11:32.239
was appointed for each group of Bible students.

01:11:32.239 --> 01:11:34.239
Now they had clear direction

01:11:34.239 --> 01:11:36.239
in following Jesus' command

01:11:36.239 --> 01:11:38.239
to preach.

01:11:38.239 --> 01:11:40.239
That convention was considered

01:11:40.239 --> 01:11:42.239
by many who were there

01:11:42.239 --> 01:11:44.239
to be the greatest ever help

01:11:44.239 --> 01:11:46.239
up to that time.

01:11:46.239 --> 01:11:48.239
So imagine their anticipation

01:11:48.239 --> 01:11:50.239
when the announcement was made

01:11:50.239 --> 01:11:52.239
of another convention

01:11:52.239 --> 01:11:54.239
in 1922.

01:11:54.239 --> 01:11:56.239
What would it bring?

01:11:56.239 --> 01:11:58.239
Would there be other

01:11:58.239 --> 01:12:00.239
exciting announcements?

01:12:00.239 --> 01:12:02.239
A-D-B, A-D-B, A-D-B?

01:12:02.239 --> 01:12:04.239
A-D-B?

01:12:04.239 --> 01:12:06.239
What is A-D-B?

01:12:06.239 --> 01:12:08.239
Many were guessing this,

01:12:08.239 --> 01:12:10.239
guessing that.

01:12:10.239 --> 01:12:12.239
Behold, the King reigns.

01:12:12.239 --> 01:12:17.680
You are his publicity agents.

01:12:17.680 --> 01:12:19.680
Therefore,

01:12:19.680 --> 01:12:21.680
advertise,

01:12:21.680 --> 01:12:23.680
advertise,

01:12:23.680 --> 01:12:25.680
advertise the King

01:12:25.680 --> 01:12:32.609
and his kingdom.

01:12:32.609 --> 01:12:34.609
Well, they want dry eyes

01:12:34.609 --> 01:12:36.609
when he was crying.

01:12:36.609 --> 01:12:38.609
Everybody was waving the

01:12:38.609 --> 01:12:40.609
anxious and talking

01:12:40.609 --> 01:12:42.609
to whoever was sitting

01:12:42.609 --> 01:12:44.609
by with a new or not.

01:12:44.609 --> 01:12:46.609
Now more than just Bible students,

01:12:46.609 --> 01:12:48.609
they were becoming an organization

01:12:48.609 --> 01:12:50.609
of preachers.

01:12:50.609 --> 01:12:52.609
What would the call

01:12:52.609 --> 01:12:54.609
to advertise the King

01:12:54.609 --> 01:12:56.609
and his kingdom lead to?

01:12:56.609 --> 01:12:58.609
What unique

01:12:58.609 --> 01:13:00.609
and innovative methods

01:13:00.609 --> 01:13:02.609
would Jehovah's people use?

01:13:02.609 --> 01:13:05.619
The next 100 years would tell the story.

01:13:05.619 --> 01:13:07.619
In 1922,

01:13:07.619 --> 01:13:09.619
Jehovah Rutherford began using

01:13:09.619 --> 01:13:11.619
the new technology of

01:13:11.619 --> 01:13:13.619
radio broadcasting,

01:13:13.619 --> 01:13:15.619
to reach a global audience

01:13:15.619 --> 01:13:17.619
with the King the Message.

01:13:17.619 --> 01:13:19.619
At its peak in 1933,

01:13:19.619 --> 01:13:21.619
radio broadcast,

01:13:21.619 --> 01:13:23.619
originating from our own

01:13:23.619 --> 01:13:25.619
WBBR studios in New York

01:13:25.619 --> 01:13:27.619
were carried by

01:13:27.619 --> 01:13:29.619
408 radio stations

01:13:29.619 --> 01:13:31.619
on six continents.

01:13:31.619 --> 01:13:33.619
But because of clergy interference,

01:13:33.619 --> 01:13:35.619
they actually denied access to their

01:13:35.619 --> 01:13:37.619
ones.

01:13:37.619 --> 01:13:39.619
Did opposition stop Jehovah's

01:13:39.619 --> 01:13:41.619
people from advertising

01:13:41.619 --> 01:13:43.619
the kingdom good news?

01:13:43.619 --> 01:13:45.619
What additional preaching methods

01:13:45.619 --> 01:13:47.619
were used?

01:13:47.619 --> 01:13:49.619
A unified, consistent message

01:13:49.619 --> 01:13:51.619
about the kingdom was achieved

01:13:51.619 --> 01:13:53.619
through the use of

01:13:53.619 --> 01:13:55.619
testimony cards in several languages.

01:13:55.619 --> 01:13:57.619
A publisher would simply

01:13:57.619 --> 01:13:59.619
hand the card to the householder

01:13:59.619 --> 01:14:01.619
and ask him to read the

01:14:01.619 --> 01:14:03.619
message.

01:14:03.619 --> 01:14:05.619
Another exciting application

01:14:05.619 --> 01:14:07.619
of technology was the use of

01:14:07.619 --> 01:14:09.619
the portable phonograph

01:14:09.619 --> 01:14:11.619
for house-to-house preaching.

01:14:11.619 --> 01:14:13.619
To expand this initiative

01:14:13.619 --> 01:14:15.619
in 1937 at the Columbus, Ohio convention,

01:14:15.619 --> 01:14:17.619
the special pioneer work was

01:14:17.619 --> 01:14:19.619
introduced.

01:14:19.619 --> 01:14:21.619
Special pioneers were encouraged

01:14:21.619 --> 01:14:23.619
to use the phonograph

01:14:23.619 --> 01:14:25.619
not only when invited

01:14:25.619 --> 01:14:27.619
into a house,

01:14:27.619 --> 01:14:29.619
but at every house.

01:14:29.619 --> 01:14:31.619
In addition,

01:14:31.619 --> 01:14:33.619
three hundred special pioneers

01:14:33.619 --> 01:14:35.619
set up the phonographs

01:14:35.619 --> 01:14:37.619
over a half a million times.

01:14:37.619 --> 01:14:39.619
Playing the pre-recorded

01:14:39.619 --> 01:14:41.619
four and a half minute talks

01:14:41.619 --> 01:14:43.619
by Brother Rutherford

01:14:43.619 --> 01:14:45.619
to over one million listeners.

01:14:45.619 --> 01:14:47.619
Other kingdom publishers

01:14:47.619 --> 01:14:49.619
thus became phonograph-minded

01:14:49.619 --> 01:14:51.619
and eventually over 47,000

01:14:51.619 --> 01:14:53.619
portable phonographs

01:14:53.619 --> 01:14:55.619
with records covering 92 topics

01:14:55.619 --> 01:14:57.619
trumpeted the kingdom message.

01:14:57.619 --> 01:14:59.619
To preach from the house-tops,

01:14:59.619 --> 01:15:01.619
Zealous Kingdom publishers

01:15:01.619 --> 01:15:03.619
amplify their ministry

01:15:03.619 --> 01:15:05.619
with transcription machines

01:15:05.619 --> 01:15:07.619
that broadcast Brother Rutherford's

01:15:07.619 --> 01:15:09.619
full length pre-recorded lectures.

01:15:09.619 --> 01:15:11.619
A transcription machine

01:15:11.619 --> 01:15:13.619
was a phonograph equipped

01:15:13.619 --> 01:15:15.619
with powered loudspeakers.

01:15:15.619 --> 01:15:17.619
This made possible sound cars

01:15:17.619 --> 01:15:19.619
and sound boats.

01:15:19.619 --> 01:15:21.619
The kingdom message was

01:15:21.619 --> 01:15:23.619
clearly heard on rivers,

01:15:23.619 --> 01:15:25.619
on streets,

01:15:25.619 --> 01:15:27.619
parks, and squares,

01:15:27.619 --> 01:15:29.619
and rented halls,

01:15:29.619 --> 01:15:31.619
theaters, and other public spaces.

01:15:31.619 --> 01:15:33.619
Equipped with tracks,

01:15:33.619 --> 01:15:35.619
booklets,

01:15:35.619 --> 01:15:37.619
magazines and books,

01:15:37.619 --> 01:15:39.619
thousands of volunteers

01:15:39.619 --> 01:15:41.619
participated in special preaching

01:15:41.619 --> 01:15:43.619
and literature distribution campaigns.

01:15:43.619 --> 01:15:45.619
These special campaigns

01:15:45.619 --> 01:15:47.619
made it possible to cover

01:15:47.619 --> 01:15:49.619
large areas with the kingdom message

01:15:49.619 --> 01:15:51.619
quickly, even in a face of opposition.

01:15:51.619 --> 01:15:53.619
Streetwork,

01:15:53.619 --> 01:15:55.619
information marches,

01:15:55.619 --> 01:15:57.619
and bicycle parades

01:15:57.619 --> 01:15:59.619
boldly brought the kingdom message

01:15:59.619 --> 01:16:01.619
directly before the eyes of the public.

01:16:01.619 --> 01:16:03.619
Marches ranged in size

01:16:03.619 --> 01:16:05.619
from just a few publishers

01:16:05.619 --> 01:16:07.619
to about a thousand publishers.

01:16:07.619 --> 01:16:09.619
Streams of kingdom publishers

01:16:09.619 --> 01:16:11.619
made their way

01:16:11.619 --> 01:16:13.619
through the business districts

01:16:13.619 --> 01:16:15.619
of large cities.

01:16:15.619 --> 01:16:17.619
They wore placards

01:16:17.619 --> 01:16:19.619
bearing a slogan,

01:16:19.619 --> 01:16:21.619
carried signs,

01:16:21.619 --> 01:16:23.619
to talk at a public meeting.

01:16:23.619 --> 01:16:25.619
While radio broadcast

01:16:25.619 --> 01:16:27.619
and information marches

01:16:27.619 --> 01:16:29.619
were an efficient way

01:16:29.619 --> 01:16:31.619
of reaching mass audiences,

01:16:31.619 --> 01:16:33.619
was it the most effective way?

01:16:33.619 --> 01:16:35.619
Our primary method of preaching,

01:16:35.619 --> 01:16:37.619
the personal door

01:16:37.619 --> 01:16:39.619
to door ministry,

01:16:39.619 --> 01:16:41.619
has proved over time

01:16:41.619 --> 01:16:43.619
to be the most effective method

01:16:43.619 --> 01:16:45.619
of advertising the kingdom.

01:16:45.619 --> 01:16:47.619
But was preaching all

01:16:47.619 --> 01:16:49.619
that was needed?

01:16:49.619 --> 01:16:51.619
That teaching others

01:16:51.619 --> 01:16:53.619
to observe all the things

01:16:53.619 --> 01:16:55.619
Jesus commanded

01:16:55.619 --> 01:16:57.619
would require training.

01:16:57.619 --> 01:16:59.619
Kingdom evangelizers

01:16:59.619 --> 01:17:01.619
needed to be trained

01:17:01.619 --> 01:17:03.619
to use the Bible effectively

01:17:03.619 --> 01:17:05.619
and to study it

01:17:05.619 --> 01:17:07.619
with interested ones.

01:17:07.619 --> 01:17:09.619
So at the call to action assembly

01:17:09.619 --> 01:17:11.619
in 1943,

01:17:11.619 --> 01:17:13.619
a new congregation meeting

01:17:13.619 --> 01:17:15.619
was announced and demonstrated.

01:17:15.619 --> 01:17:17.619
It was called

01:17:17.619 --> 01:17:19.619
soon textbooks

01:17:19.619 --> 01:17:21.619
were released to help our brothers

01:17:21.619 --> 01:17:23.619
cultivate their teaching skills.

01:17:23.619 --> 01:17:25.619
The books Theocratic Aid

01:17:25.619 --> 01:17:27.619
published in 1945

01:17:27.619 --> 01:17:29.619
provided clear guidance

01:17:29.619 --> 01:17:31.619
for improved public speaking,

01:17:31.619 --> 01:17:33.619
effective door-to-door witnessing,

01:17:33.619 --> 01:17:35.619
making meaningful return visits

01:17:35.619 --> 01:17:37.619
and conducting progressive Bible studies.

01:17:37.619 --> 01:17:39.619
While equipped for every good work,

01:17:39.619 --> 01:17:41.619
released in 1946,

01:17:41.619 --> 01:17:43.619
laid a solid foundation

01:17:43.619 --> 01:17:45.619
of Bible truth through an in-depth

